headline: 1 Industrials Stock to Target This Week and 2 to Brush Off
summary: Whether you see them or not, industrials businesses play a crucial part in our daily activities. Unfortunately, this role also comes with a demand profile tethered to the ebbs and flows of the broader economy, and investors seem to be forecasting a downturn - over the past six months, the industry has pulled back by 12.1%. This drawdown was worse than the S&P 500’s 5.2% fall.
